FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773194862
OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'step change' in
OL,4,Csupport for veterans with TBI
OL,6,FIn an interview with ITV News
OL,7,Fpresenter Mary Nightingale, the
OL,8,Fminister said a #50 million investment
OL,9,Fin "joining up" services designed to
OL,10,Fsupport veterans who are struggling
OL,11,Fwith TBI and other issues would
OL,12,Fdeliver real change.
OL,14,FThe programme, called Operation
OL,15,FValour, will launch later this year.
OL,17,FOver the past 18 months, ITV News has
OL,18,Fbeen reporting the issue of Blast
OL,19,FInduced TBI in military veterans.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773194862
OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'step change' in
OL,4,Csupport for veterans with TBI
OL,6,FResearch in the US and elsewhere shows
OL,7,Fthat repeated exposure to low-level
OL,8,Fblast can cause long-term neurological
OL,9,Fdamage. This includes past exposure to
OL,10,Fveterans' own weapons, particular
OL,11,Fartillery, mortars and shoulder-
OL,12,Flaunched anti-tank missiles.
OL,14,FWe have highlighted numerous cases
OL,15,Fwhere British veterans who have been
OL,16,Fexposed to blasts and have suffered
OL,17,Fphysical neurological damage have been
OL,18,Fmisdiagnosed with psychiatric
OL,19,Fconditions, most commonly PTSD.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773194862
OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'step change' in
OL,4,Csupport for veterans with TBI
OL,6,FMrs Sandher-Jones, who served in
OL,7,FAfghanistan with the Intelligence
OL,8,FCorps before entering politics, said:
OL,9,F"It's so difficult for me as veterans
OL,10,Fminister when I meet so many people
OL,11,Fwho are struggling with a multitude of
OL,12,Fchallenges and sadly, some people can
OL,13,Fface more than one challenge...
OL,15,F"It's really, really, a priority of
OL,16,Fmine to make sure that we're able to
OL,17,Fgive support to veterans...that's why
OL,18,Fwe're launching Valour, which is a #50
OL,19,Fmillion commitment, which is about
OL,20,Fcoordinating support for veterans."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773194862
OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'step change' in
OL,4,Csupport for veterans with TBI
OL,6,FVeterans who have spoken to ITV News
OL,7,Fhighlight the difficulty of getting a
OL,8,Fblast-related TBI diagnosis through
OL,9,Fthe NHS and say there is no NHS care
OL,10,Fpathway specific to the condition.
OL,12,FThe Minister said: "When it comes to
OL,13,Ftreatment, there's a whole range of
OL,14,Fservices out there. We have Op Courage
OL,15,Fand Op Restore, which give specialised
OL,16,Ftreatment pathways through the NHS. We
OL,17,Fdo have two compensation schemes
OL,18,Fdepending on when you serve, where
OL,19,Ftraumatic brain injuries is included.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773194862
OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'step change' in
OL,4,Csupport for veterans with TBI
OL,6,F"We've got these research programmes
OL,7,Fthat are going ahead looking into
OL,8,FTraumatic Brain Injuries. We also have
OL,9,Fcross-government work looking at
OL,10,FTraumatic Brain Injuries, that's going
OL,11,Fon as well."
OL,13,FWe asked the Minister why tens of
OL,14,Fthousands of American veterans have a
OL,15,FBlast TBI diagnosis compared with a
OL,16,Fvanishingly small number of British
OL,17,Fveterans. She pointed to differences
OL,18,Fin medical care systems between the
OL,19,Ftwo countries as an explanation for
OL,20,Fthe difference in diagnosis rates.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773194862
OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'step change' in
OL,4,Csupport for veterans with TBI
OL,6,FShe said the government is committed
OL,7,Fto researching Blast TBI but should be
OL,8,Fcautious in taking specific action to
OL,9,Fhelp until more research is completed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773194862
OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'step change' in
OL,4,Csupport for veterans with TBI
OL,6,FShe said: "We've spent three and a
OL,7,Fhalf million pounds on the world's
OL,8,Ffirst mobile scanner which does brain
OL,9,Fscans, we're going to be rolling that
OL,10,Fout hopefully very soon, taking that
OL,11,Fdown to troops exercising on Salisbury
OL,12,FPlain, on firing ranges, places like
OL,13,Fthat so we can be able to scan
OL,14,Fsoldiers just as they've been doing
OL,15,Ftheir activities and in the immediate
OL,16,Faftermath as well so we can really
OL,17,Fstart to gather that evidence to look
OL,18,Fat any changes that happen (in the
OL,19,Fbrain).
OL,26,@zD@\pm{D@Fpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773194862
OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'step change' in
OL,4,Csupport for veterans with TBI
OL,6,F"In order to understand some of the
OL,7,Flonger term impacts of brain injuries,
OL,8,Fit's helpful to be able to see in the
OL,9,Fimmediate aftermath of working with
OL,10,Fexplosives, for example. Obviously we
OL,11,Fcan't go back in time and be able to
OL,12,Fdo that on veteran cohort that served,
OL,13,Fyou know, perhaps when I was serving,
OL,14,Fbut that information is going to be
OL,15,Freally, really helpful for us to
OL,16,Funderstand the longer term impacts."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773194862
OL,3,CGovernment pledges 'step change' in
OL,4,Csupport for veterans with TBI
OL,6,F"I've got to make sure that we're
OL,7,Ffollowing the science here. I'm
OL,8,Fkeeping track of the progress of these
OL,9,Fstudies very closely, making sure that
OL,10,FI'm getting the updates that I need to
OL,11,Fhave and where we need to act, we will
OL,12,Fact as swiftly as we can."
